716
00:50:22,128 --> 00:50:23,713
就在那
Right over there.

717
00:50:27,133 --> 00:50:29,094
你真是個寶寶
Aren't you a sweetie.

718
00:50:43,525 --> 00:50:45,402
打擾一下 我們見過嗎
I'm sorry, have we met?

719
00:50:45,443 --> 00:50:47,195
沒有
Not exactly.

720
00:50:47,237 --> 00:50:48,071
奧利維亞
Olivia.

721
00:50:49,447 --> 00:50:51,283
-傑克遜 -謝依我知道的
- Jackson. - Shea, yes.

722
00:50:59,666 --> 00:51:02,294
馬丁比格是我們共同的朋友
Martin Bigg was a mutual friend.

723
00:51:07,424 --> 00:51:09,926
放心我不是警察
Oh don't worry, I'm not a cop.

724
00:51:12,138 --> 00:51:15,598
不過你對貝爾蒙特做出的事 可夠勁兒的
But that was quite a job you did on Belmont.

725
00:51:15,640 --> 00:51:17,517
你怎麼知道就是我幹的
Who says that was me?

726
00:51:18,643 --> 00:51:20,312
我自有方法
I have my sources.

727
00:51:22,105 --> 00:51:25,275
我不喜歡被別人跟著
I don't like being followed.

728
00:51:25,317 --> 00:51:26,151
看出來了
Noted.

729
00:51:32,824 --> 00:51:33,992
和我跳舞吧
Dance with me.

730
00:51:39,497 --> 00:51:43,084
你當不了警察一定是因為你大美了
And you're too pretty to be a cop.

731
00:51:53,762 --> 00:51:55,305
我不認識馬丁
I didn't know Martin.

732
00:51:55,347 --> 00:51:58,099
但我的父親跟他很熟
But my father, very close to him.

733
00:52:00,977 --> 00:52:03,229
你父親是誰
Who's your father?

734
00:52:04,647 --> 00:52:05,857
查理·羅斯
Charlie Rose.

735
00:52:08,693 --> 00:52:09,861
和你一樣
Just like you.

736
00:52:11,446 --> 00:52:13,114
他也是個商人
He's a business man.

737
00:52:14,657 --> 00:52:16,493
哪種商人
What kinda business?

738
00:52:19,621 --> 00:52:20,872
收購業
Acquisitions.

739
00:52:25,210 --> 00:52:28,838
你怎麼知道在哪可以找到我的
How'd you know where to find me?

740
00:52:28,880 --> 00:52:31,424
看看這周圍
You seen this place?

741
00:52:31,466 --> 00:52:35,303
只要有新人 我就會知道
Somebody new walks into town, I hear about it.

742
00:52:36,805 --> 00:52:40,975
另外 小貝利可是我的人
Besides, little Billy over there has a sweet spot for me.

743
00:52:55,448 --> 00:52:56,950
想那啥不
Wanna take a ride?

744
00:52:58,910 --> 00:53:00,120
帶路
Lead the way.

745
00:53:45,957 --> 00:53:47,876
-嗨 姑娘們 -早上好
- Hi ladies. - Good morning.

746
00:53:47,917 --> 00:53:50,670
-嘿 爸爸 -我女兒醒了
- Hey Daddy. - Well, my daughter's awake.

747
00:53:50,712 --> 00:53:52,881
爸爸 這是傑克·謝依
Daddy, meet Jack Shea.

748
00:53:52,922 --> 00:53:54,507
傑克 這是查理
Jack, meet Charlie.

749
00:53:55,800 --> 00:53:56,676
羅斯先生
Mr. Rose.

750
00:53:58,261 --> 00:54:01,431
馬蒂從來沒說過你是這樣的老手
Marty never said you were such a city slicker.

751
00:54:01,473 --> 00:54:03,933
有問題嗎
Is that gonna be a problem?

752
