不 沒問題 除非你不安分
No, not a problem, unless you make it that way.

753
00:54:08,813 --> 00:54:11,357
你們現在還沒在一起 對吧
You all didn't do nothing together, now, did you?

754
00:54:11,399 --> 00:54:12,400
噢 爸爸
Oh, Daddy.

755
00:54:13,526 --> 00:54:16,654
好了 我只是和你開玩笑
Oh, come on, I'm just playing with you.

756
00:54:16,696 --> 00:54:19,949
過來聊一會
Come on over here and chat for a while.

757
00:54:25,705 --> 00:54:30,543
姑娘們 你們為什麼不進屋涼快去呢
Ladies, why don't you go on inside and cool off a bit?

758
00:54:30,585 --> 00:54:32,045
哦 寶貝
Aw, baby.

759
00:54:32,086 --> 00:54:33,546
-哈爾 -是的 老闆
- Hal? - Yes sir.

760
00:54:33,588 --> 00:54:35,882
姑娘們 請離開游泳池 馬上
Ladies, outta the pool, now.

761
00:54:38,510 --> 00:54:42,805
你知道我很喜歡年輕的活力
You know I like to harness the energy of youth.

762
00:54:42,847 --> 00:54:44,390
來瓶啤酒嗎
You want a beer?

763
00:54:44,432 --> 00:54:47,268
聽著 羅斯先生 我來這的原因是
Look, Mr. Rose, the only reason I'm here

764
00:54:47,310 --> 00:54:49,646
馬蒂說他在德克薩斯州有個朋友
is because Marty said he had a friend in Texas,

765
00:54:49,687 --> 00:54:50,855
就是這樣
and that's it.

766
00:54:52,482 --> 00:54:55,485
馬蒂就是個爛好人
Marty, Marty was thick as a brick.

767
00:54:56,611 --> 00:55:00,406
但他對人的判斷很準
But he was a tremendous judge of character.

768
00:55:00,448 --> 00:55:04,285
表面來看 你是達標的
Now, from appearance, you look like you're up to the mark,

769
00:55:04,327 --> 00:55:07,705
但我關心的是內在
but it's what's underneath that concerns me.

770
00:55:07,747 --> 00:55:11,584
如果你只是有勇無謀
If you'll crack when the heat gets cranked up.

771
00:55:15,547 --> 00:55:18,091
你也不會有什麼出息
You gotta keep a low profile.

772
00:55:18,132 --> 00:55:19,676
我這一生
I've been my entire life,

773
00:55:19,717 --> 00:55:23,930
什麼都嘗試過
and I never got so much as a hockey ticket.

774
00:55:24,289 --> 00:55:26,349
除了賭馬和石油
I only do outside horses and oil,

775
00:55:26,391 --> 00:55:29,930
我不在住的地方拉屎 你要明白我的意圖
and I don't shit where I live, if you catch my drift.

776
00:55:30,228 --> 00:55:34,399
我花了一整年的時間 只做一件事
I spend a whole year, an entire year, on a single project.

777
00:55:35,567 --> 00:55:38,403
但是報酬一直可觀
But the payoff is always worthwhile.

778
00:55:40,697 --> 00:55:42,282
價值少於500萬
And I don't touching nothing,

779
00:55:42,323 --> 00:55:46,703
我不會動手
unless it'll fetch at least five million U.S.

780
00:55:46,744 --> 00:55:49,414
我有一個團隊 大家輪流做隊長
I use a crew, and I rotate who's in charge.

781
00:55:49,455 --> 00:55:52,709
當奧利維亞不製造混亂時
Olivia there sometimes acts as another guy,

782
00:55:52,750 --> 00:55:55,169
她也會一樣的出任務
when she's not causing chaos.

783
00:56:00,758 --> 00:56:04,679
要知道 我從不用來自德克薩斯以外的人
You know, I never hire a man unless they're a Texas man.

784
00:56:04,721 --> 00:56:06,180
我只是不信任他們
I just don't trust 'em.

785
00:56:06,222 --> 00:56:09,267
但是馬緹和我親如兄弟
But Marty was a brother to me.

786
00:56:09,309 --> 00:56:11,936
所以我不會把你丟出去
So I'm not gonna throw you out.

787
00:56:13,688 --> 00:56:16,899
但你必須證明你自己
But you're gonna have to prove yourself.

788
00:56:16,941 --> 00:56:19,861
你認為怎麼樣
What do you think there, blue eyes?

789
00:56:29,245 --> 00:56:31,289
我們什麼時候開始
When do we get started?

790
00:56:34,083 --> 00:56:36,085
7千5百萬怎麼樣
How does 75 mil sound?

791
00:57:02,560 --> 00:57:05,740
下午好 斯特伯諾維特茲先生 和太太
Good afternoon, Mr. and Ms. Stroblekowitz.

792
00:57:05,782 --> 00:57:07,784
-今天怎麼樣 -很好 謝謝
How're y'all doing today? - Very well, thank you.

793
00:57:07,825 --> 00:57:09,327
比克爾先生已經在等你們了
Mr. Beeker's ready for you.

794
00:57:09,369 --> 00:57:11,204
弗林會帶你們去樓上
Flynn'll be taking you upstairs.

795
00:57:11,245 --> 00:57:12,955
請跟我來
Please follow me.

796
00:57:12,997 --> 00:57:14,415
-謝謝你 -祝心情愉快
- Thank you. - Y'all have a great day.

797
00:57:14,457 --> 00:57:16,292
-謝謝 -謝謝
- Thank you. - Thank you.

798
00:57:16,334 --> 00:57:18,586
西蒙·貝克爾 你所聽說過的
Simon Beeker was the president of the largest bank

799
00:57:18,628 --> 00:57:21,130
最大銀行的總裁
nobody ever heard of.

800
00:57:21,172 --> 00:57:25,009
貝克爾掌握著跨洋的金融業務
Beeker handled overseas financial transactions,

801
00:57:25,051 --> 00:57:27,470
以及資金的流向
how the money flowed.

802
00:57:27,512 --> 00:57:30,431
貝克爾沒有獲得一點利益
Just none of it flowed to Beeker.

803
00:57:30,473 --> 00:57:34,477
貝克爾先生 你的客人到了
Mr. Beeker, your clients have arrived.

804
00:57:36,813 --> 00:57:37,647
嗨
Hi.

805
00:57:38,648 --> 00:57:39,565
下午好
Afternoon.

806
00:57:39,607 --> 00:57:42,443
-請坐 -謝謝
- Please, have a seat. - Thank you.

807
00:57:44,987 --> 00:57:46,489
有什麼可以幫你的
What can I do for you?

808
00:57:46,531 --> 00:57:49,534
我們代表羅斯先生
We represent Mr. Rose's interests.

809
00:57:53,871 --> 00:57:54,914
是的 貝克爾先生
Yes, Mr. Beeker.

810
00:57:54,956 --> 00:57:57,375
櫻桃 你能讓保羅進來嗎
Cherry, can you send Paul in, please?

811
00:57:57,417 --> 00:57:58,543
馬上
Right away.

812
00:58:00,878 --> 00:58:01,713
嗯
Um.

813
00:58:03,798 --> 00:58:04,424
我
I, uh,

814
00:58:05,758 --> 00:58:08,094
我沒想到你這麼快
I didn't expect you so soon.

815
00:58:11,222 --> 00:58:13,391
時間加快了
The timeline's moved up.

816
00:58:35,997 --> 00:58:37,498
好了 貝克爾先生
Now, Mr. Beeker.

817
00:58:39,792 --> 00:58:43,296
地下室的密碼每天都換
We know the Vault's codes change daily.

818
00:58:43,337 --> 00:58:45,298
你的人在晚上十一點出現
Now your man, they show up at 11:00 PM,

819
00:58:45,339 --> 00:58:47,633
非常準時
not a second sooner or later,

820
00:58:47,675 --> 00:58:49,385
輸入密碼 我們就能過上好日子
with the codes, and we're golden.

821
00:58:49,427 --> 00:58:53,556
之後 我們就可以頤養天年了
Anything after that, we're not gonna do business.

822
00:58:55,516 --> 00:58:56,809
貝克爾先生
Now, Mr. Beeker.

823
00:58:56,851 --> 00:59:01,230
地下室裏有價值7干5百萬的債券
We know that there's 75 million in bonds in that vault.

824
00:59:02,690 --> 00:59:04,984
7干5百萬 聽起來太棒了
75 mil sounds good.

825
00:59:05,026 --> 00:59:06,903
這次 我要做領隊
But this time I'm the leading man.

826
00:59:06,944 --> 00:59:09,530
-噢 不女士 你不行 -先生 我行的
- No ma'am, you are not. - Oh yes sir, I am.

827
00:59:09,572 --> 00:59:11,991
希望你能原諒 但是你不行
I beg your pardon, missy, but you are not.

828
00:59:12,033 --> 00:59:12,867
爸爸
Daddy.

829
00:59:15,578 --> 00:59:16,412
好吧
. Okay

830
00:59:17,330 --> 00:59:20,416
各退一步吧 小姑娘
You wanna wheel and deal, missy?

831
00:59:20,458 --> 00:59:22,168
你帶上哈爾
You take Hal.

832
00:59:22,210 --> 00:59:24,086
我懂 老闆
Got you, boss.

833
00:59:24,128 --> 00:59:26,798
我會好好照顧她的
I'll take real good care of her.

834
00:59:29,592 --> 00:59:31,761
不 我不會帶哈爾
No, I am not taking Hal.

835
00:59:33,429 --> 00:59:34,931
你真不帶
Do we have a deal?

836
00:59:36,098 --> 00:59:38,726
羅斯先生的分利是10%
Mr. Rose's cut is 10 cents on the dollar.

837
00:59:38,768 --> 00:59:40,645
聽明白了嗎
Do I make myself clear?

838
00:59:44,065 --> 00:59:46,067
是的 明白了
Yeah, that's understood.

839
00:59:46,108 --> 00:59:50,947
好吧 合作愉快
Alright then, pleasure doing business with you.

840
00:59:50,988 --> 00:59:52,740
好吧 成交 不帶哈爾
Okay, deal, no Hal.

841
00:59:55,576 --> 00:59:57,078
-乾杯 -乾杯
- Cheers. - Cheers.

842
01:00:11,050 --> 01:00:13,302
很開心
I was happy.

843
01:00:13,344 --> 01:00:15,847
就像是 第一次
It seemed like, just for once,

844
01:00:17,014 --> 01:00:19,475
我得到了上帝的眷顧
God smiled down on me.

845
01:00:19,517 --> 01:00:22,144
你知道我多愛你嗎
You know how much I love you?

846
01:00:24,188 --> 01:00:25,815
我很愛你
I love you so much.

847
01:00:34,282 --> 01:00:36,033
我對你至死不渝
I love you forever.

848
01:00:51,340 --> 01:00:52,842
是的
Yeah.

849
01:00:52,884 --> 01:00:55,177
我有個活 需要一個司機
I got a job, I need a driver.

850
01:00:55,219 --> 01:00:56,679
讓我來
Yeah, I can drive.

851
01:00:56,721 --> 01:00:57,430
我能得多少
How much?

852
01:00:57,471 --> 01:00:59,515
正常水平
The usual amount.

853
01:00:59,557 --> 01:01:00,850
什麼時候開始
What time do y'all need me there?

854
01:01:00,892 --> 01:01:02,184
這幾天吧
Couple days.

855
01:01:02,226 --> 01:01:03,561
保持手機通暢
Keep your phone on.

856
01:01:03,603 --> 01:01:05,021
隨時聽候
I'll be in touch.

857
01:01:06,856 --> 01:01:07,690
好了
It's done.

858
01:01:12,904 --> 01:01:15,740
有時你得把韁繩抓在手裏
Sometimes you gotta keep the training wheels on,

859
01:01:15,781 --> 01:01:18,618
即使它們想自由
even though they wanna roll alone.

860
01:01:47,438 --> 01:01:49,231
我們包圍了這裏
We cased the place.

861
01:01:49,273 --> 01:01:51,359
我們有設計圖 守衛時間表
We had blueprints, guard schedules,

862
01:01:51,392 --> 01:01:54,243
查理甚至弄來了安全系統的備份
and Charlie even had a duplicate

863
01:01:54,314 --> 01:01:56,405
來給我練習
of the security system made for me to practice.

864
01:01:56,447 --> 01:01:59,241
一切準備就緒
We had all the bases covered.

865
01:01:59,283 --> 01:02:00,618
好的
Okay.

866
01:02:14,382 --> 01:02:16,149
我們穿的像去參加葬禮一樣
We look like we're dressed for a funeral.

867
01:02:16,454 --> 01:02:17,885
我看見你把兄弟們帶來了
I see you brought your boyfriends,

868
01:02:17,927 --> 01:02:18,719
密碼帶了嗎
did you bring the codes?

869
01:02:18,761 --> 01:02:20,554
這就是我們來這的原因 傑克
That's why we're here, Jack.

870
01:02:20,596 --> 01:02:22,682
那麼開始幹活吧
Then let's get to work.

871
01:02:23,891 --> 01:02:26,435
-嘿 -直盯著掃瞄器好嗎
Hey, keep an eye on the scanners, alright?

872
01:02:26,477 --> 01:02:29,397
確保無死角監控
Make sure all the edges are sealed.

873
01:02:53,671 --> 01:02:55,131
這是貝克爾的私人樓層
This is Beeker's private floor.

874
01:02:55,172 --> 01:02:57,174
沒有攝像頭
There's no cameras here.

875
01:02:59,176 --> 01:03:00,261
走這邊
There you go.

876
01:03:01,766 --> 01:03:03,254
貝克爾用攝像頭
Beeker put the security cameras

877
01:03:03,265 --> 01:03:06,027
把金庫全方位的監控起來了
in the vault on loop.

878
01:03:07,184 --> 01:03:08,019
幹得好
Nice.

879
01:03:11,105 --> 01:03:12,401
我們爭取了一小時
We got an hour,

880
01:03:12,412 --> 01:03:14,993
然後貝克爾來分他的那一份
then Beeker will be here to get his cut.

881
01:03:21,782 --> 01:03:22,616
密碼
Codes.

882
01:03:24,702 --> 01:03:25,578
給
Here.

883
01:03:27,637 --> 01:03:29,473
如果其中一個數字是錯的
If even one of those numbers is wrong,

884
01:03:29,497 --> 01:03:31,333
