Pressure changes things.

889
01:03:38,632 --> 01:03:42,178
讓一個人寫6而不是9
Makes a man write a six instead of a nine.

890
01:03:42,219 --> 01:03:44,388
不是貝克爾 他很堅強
Not Beeker, the man's ice.

891
01:03:44,430 --> 01:03:46,849
我說的是你
I was talking about you.

892
