1257
01:37:26,040 --> 01:37:27,451
我經過 那幽溪山谷
Yea, though I walk through

1258
01:37:27,493 --> 01:37:29,453
死亡的影子鋪陳其上
the valley of the shadow of death,

1259
01:37:29,495 --> 01:37:32,873
我不畏魔鬼 因你在身旁
I will fear no evil, for thou art with me.

1260
01:37:32,915 --> 01:37:36,168
你的棍杖 來撫慰我的心
Thy rod and thy staff, they comfort me,

1261
01:37:36,210 --> 01:37:37,961
再難言 仁慈與善良
surely the goodness of mercy

1262
01:37:38,003 --> 01:37:40,964
它們追隨至我生命盡頭
shall follow me all the days of my life.

1263
01:37:41,006 --> 01:37:45,177
我將終日憩息在主的蔭蔽下
And I will dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

1264
01:38:19,128 --> 01:38:22,297
有什麼遺言嗎 謝伊
Any last words, Shea?

1265
01:38:55,312 --> 01:38:57,689
最糟糕的是
he worst part is,

1266
01:38:57,919 --> 01:39:01,005
沒人會來為我送行
nobody's gonna be there to see me off.

1267
01:39:06,991 --> 01:39:11,514
拒絕簽特赦令
*

1268
01:39:51,511 --> 01:39:52,554
我愛你
I love you.

1269
01:39:59,603 --> 01:40:01,104
你很快就和我在一起了
I'll see you soon.

1270
01:40:59,079 --> 01:40:59,955
暴力
Violence.

1271
01:41:00,956 --> 01:41:02,457
由什麼引起的
What is the cause?

1272
01:41:03,421 --> 01:41:05,502
要真正的瞭解暴力的本質
To truly understand the nature of violence,

1273
01:41:05,544 --> 01:41:08,004
我們要超越個體地去看待它
we need to look beyond the individual.

1274
01:41:08,714 --> 01:41:10,507
我們要去瞭解
We need to look at the culture of violence

1275
01:41:10,549 --> 01:41:12,342
滲透進我們社會的 暴力文化
that permeates our society.

1276
01:41:12,384 --> 01:41:13,593
我們同樣也需要瞭解
And we also need to look at the way

1277
01:41:13,635 --> 01:41:16,221
暴力的懲罰方式
that we punish those that commit acts of violence.

1278
01:41:16,263 --> 01:41:19,057
因為當我們以暴制暴
Because when we answer violence with violence

1279
01:41:19,099 --> 01:41:21,226
殺人償命的時候
and trade death for death,

1280
01:41:21,268 --> 01:41:25,689
我們只是在加重惡性循環
all we're doing is perpetuating a vicious cycle.

1281
01:41:25,731 --> 01:41:27,566
但假如你愛的人被謀殺了呢
But what if someone you love was murdered?

1282
01:41:27,607 --> 01:41:28,608
你會認為
Would you feel that answering

1283
01:41:28,650 --> 01:41:31,987
以暴制暴才是正確的事嗎
violence with violence is appropriate?

1284
01:41:42,372 --> 01:41:45,167
我相信在那一瞬間我會有這種想法
I believe I would feel that in the moment.

1285
01:41:45,208 --> 01:41:46,585
但我不希望他們的死
But I wouldn't want their deaths avenged

1286
01:41:46,626 --> 01:41:49,338
在一個殘忍而無常的體系裏 得到復仇
by a cruel and capricious system.

